      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "Gah... Coordinating a fleet is harder than I expected...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "level",
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "All the planes are operating properly, and I should also be in good shape, but... What's going on...?!",
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "Is there some limit to the commanding and operational abilities of light carriers...?",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107380,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "If I may say something, Independence...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "paintingFadeOut": {
        "time": 0.5,
        "side": 0
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "You're the historian... Shangri-La?",
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107380,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 4,
      "say": "Yes. I beg your pardon, but as the observer, I'd like to break the problems that you're currently facing...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "While there are no problems with your aircraft, the main line has advanced too far forward and you've gotten separated from the sentry ships.",
      "actor": 107380,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107380,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "Aren't you... acting a bit rash? I'm afraid you'll rush headfirst into trouble if you press forward with the way things are right now...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "I'm... being rash? I see. Thank you for your advice.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "You're welcome. Anyway, I still have work to do.",
      "actor": 107380,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "Working together as a team, huh...",
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "(I'm going to have to prioritize that if I want a shot at taking on Essex. But how do I do that...?)",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 102090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "Hmm? Whatcha doing, Independence? You look like something's really bothering you.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 67.5,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.2,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "(Cleveland...? I wonder if I should ask her for some tips... As the lead ship of her class, I'm sure she knows something...)",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "To be honest...",
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 102090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "flashout": {
        "alpha": [
          0,
          1
        ],
        "black": true,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "Gotcha. So you want to improve the fleet's teamwork...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-1",
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 102090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "About that...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 0,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.4,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 22.5
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "You don't know much about that either, right? After all, you're the one always charging ahead of the rest of us. Hehe~",
      "actor": 102100,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "Works out though. Cleve's the strongest, so she has no problem destroying all the enemies by herself.",
      "actor": 102140,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 102090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "Huh? When'd you all get here?",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "We were here the whole time?",
      "actor": 102150,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "(The girls who were supposed to be my sister ships... Cleveland, Columbia, Montpelier, and Denver... they're all here?)",
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "...Looks like we can't come up with any good ideas even with all three of us here... Ahaha!",
      "actor": 102150,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "I feel like as well as we communicate and get to know each other better, that'll naturally carry over to our ability to cooperate during battle as well.",
      "actor": 102150,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "Independence, you were just assigned here, right? Lemme show you around port, c'mon!",
      "actor": 102150,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "Huh, right now? But the drill's right after--",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "Don't sweat the small stuff! It's okay, the commander will totally understand!",
      "actor": 102100,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "F-fine...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "All right, shall we head out then?",
      "actor": 102090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "actor": 102090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "...Wait, what the heck! She was asking me for advice, and I couldn't come up with anything useful at all!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "Don't worry about it, Cleve. You'll get another chance!",
      "actor": 102140,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nepu1"
    },
    {
      "say": "......",
      "actor": 107220,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
